data.description:
Welcome to this exceptional 4 bdrm gem, that once served as the model home for this prestigious community.  This home seamlessly combines modern living with classic design, showcasing the builder's commitment to quality and style.

Elegant living spaces will greet you upon entry, with wood flooring, granite counters in the kitchen, w/ 42'' upgraded cabinets and stainless steel appliances.  This home includes front and back covered porches, a fire pit surrounded by elegant sealed pavers and meticulous landscape.

Upstairs boasts a HUGE loft, walk-in closets, upgraded light fixtures, staircase and a serene master suite.  Relax to the upgraded sounds via the internal surround sound.

Live in this sought-after community and enjoy top rated schools, parks and dining.
